 <instruction>Nym <ingredient en="pork" commodity="Q191768">sweinein fleisch</ingredient> hertte <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> <ingredient en="common sage" commodity="Q1111359">Saluay</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="herb" commodity="Q207123">kraut</ingredient></instruction>
 <instruction>hakch das alles zusamen</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>full In damit den <ingredient commodity="Q107246439" en="bustard neck">hals</ingredient></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>sewd In</instruction>
 <instruction>so er gar sey gesotten So leg In also haissen auff den <tool en="grate" commodity="Q96279691">rost</tool></instruction>
 <instruction>peslach In <alternative reason="ingredient">mit <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayren</ingredient> oder mit <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> <ingredient en="batter" commodity="Q29493">taig</ingredient></alternative></instruction>
 <instruction>petrewffen mit <ingredient en="lard" commodity="Q72827">smalcz</ingredient></instruction>
 So <instruction>nym <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">Saffran</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="parsley" commodity="Q25284">peter sill</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="fennel" commodity="Q27658833">phenich</ingredient></instruction>
 <instruction>mal das auff ein <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">Condiment</dish> So du pest macht</instruction>
 vnd <closer>gib es hyn</closer> </div></body></text></TEI>